{"tid":1916294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 豬嘴係有佢優勝於口罩之處","createTime":"2020-03-08T18:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T18:36:59.000Z","uid":167802,"like":72,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"fd90240b20d9513c005322a19dc403ade80bba0a","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:56:46.000Z","msg":"呢兩日見倒幾個po話唔好戴豬嘴出街，話同口罩一鳩樣但又可能會招致<span style=\"color: red;\">殺身之禍。呢點我理解嘅，不過喺度唔放大縮細討論，大家自行衡量。</span>不過喺防疫方面只要正確使用，generally豬咀有潛質係個更好嘅選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 氣密性超班</span></strong></span><br />\n平時睇到啲外科口罩標示<span style=\"color: gold;\">BFE PFE VFE 99%</span>甚至以上，係咪覺得佢哋好勁呢? 咁當然唔係話口罩無效啦。但係知唔知道個test係點做? <span style=\"color: violet;\">係對正個罩嚟做架!</span> 飛沫可以繞過口罩正面，從4個方向進入並且污染口罩內部甚至吸入體內。如果個測試啲飛沫係由唔同方向射向口罩嘅話，個<span style=\"color: violet;\">過濾率可以得番7,8成架咋</span>!<br />\n至於N95，有用開嘅人都知道係要做fit test先知要咩size，而且唔易戴得啱、唔易做到真正氣密!<br />\n但豬嘴嘅設計因為<span style=\"color: gold;\">彈性嘅塑膠/矽膠設計</span>，大部份人用都可以容易達致氣密效果，而且仲唔會有口罩超常見嘅上方鐵線位漏氣嘅問題。只有喺氣密嘅情況下，果個filter嘅efficiency，先真正等於個filter自身嘅efficiency!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 價錢</span></strong></span><br />\n覺得豬嘴肯定貴? 隻價偏貴我駁唔倒啦，但其實大家留意吓，而家網上啲口罩都炒到<span style=\"color: red;\">至少5蚊隻以上</span>，連運費<span style=\"color: red;\">破40蚊</span>嘅我都見過。防護用N95呢，<span style=\"color: red;\">1x蚊隻以上</span>係基本啦。而且仲係要日日換，甚至濕起上嚟一日用兩個，條數其實都好甘。良心貨唔係無，但大家都知真係買少見少，全部大排長龍，我就一定留畀啲有需要人士呀，老人家果啲先。<br />\n豬嘴而家都炒。但學袁教授話齋，唔到年尾都唔好唔戴，果個可以清潔重用嘅嘴雖然都炒到3百幾，但圍番起當你2蚊日好未? 至於個filter，以都係炒到3百幾4百蚊一對嘅60926為例，當你雙嘴用四星期，畀夠你400蚊，除番都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">每日15蚊</span>。以高防嚟講其實真係唔算貴呀! <span style=\"color: gold;\">(另外我知最近有人批3D印緊啲可以剪外科口罩filter擺入去用嘅3M豬嘴filter匣，都係幾十蚊一對。因為可以將一片口罩剪開多次用，價錢將會抵過口罩，但同時因為氣密緣故防禦力又高過口罩!)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 豬嘴係自私道具?</span></strong></span><br />\n當然豬嘴有一個大家都知嘅問題，就係佢哋好多嘅設計個出氣口係經另一閥而唔經filter，所以如果你係隱形患者，咁香港人就真係多得你唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 目前由於3M豬嘴出氣口設計各異，所以(好似係)仲未有人開發倒出氣口嘅filter匣，但其實大家係可以用番上面個方法，搵一片剪啱size形狀嘅外科口罩喺個出口位度貼實佢。 (我唔係專家，但以防droplets嚟講，咁樣都應該係有效嘅?)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">4. 舒適度</span></strong></span><br />\n我覺得似乎個個人嘅感覺唔同，我都不便一口咬定，但我真係覺得豬嘴係最舒服嘅。首先N95就一定係好唔舒服嘅，因為出入都會經過個高阻力嘅filter。我自己戴半個鐘經已覺得好難頂。(你覺得戴N95抖氣好順暢? 恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無氣密，衰過無戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 但豬嘴就相對通風相當好，至少呼氣一定好順暢，而我自己覺得吸氣都只係差無戴嘴少少 (有test氣密，無漏氣的)。外科口罩有時會搞到我面頰同埋個鼻好痕，同埋眼鏡經常起霧。所以我個人rating一定係豬嘴第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">5. 保護手足</span></strong></span><br />\n呢個大家應該明，我就唔畫出腸喇。越多人戴越好。<br />\n<br />\n小小建議<br />\n希望能夠入手嘅都可以考慮下用豬嘴<br />\n記得做好清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面好多懶人包我就唔再詳細講喇"},{"pid":"15f291b654bc0afca132ce7b6f4f83619daba82e","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:57:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abdd2492039c5b8aadcc1a0827323570884e91bb","tid":1916294,"uid":267513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a3ca34b0317dfaa528e09a75c39232c6620dda","tid":1916294,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:58:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76ae98b2547a590d3bf790ec9c1d0b45238cfc79","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"083eef72f2d47d2c5d940d6d57603d21302dac88","tid":1916294,"uid":42764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:59:40.000Z","msg":"環保"},{"pid":"843bf1e227bbbb933fb5b4c36a5e11783ad6c816","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd993526f9df20198f7d8dac0b972d0fe833fb8d","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"083eef72f2d47d2c5d940d6d57603d21302dac88","tid":1916294,"uid":42764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:59:40.000Z","msg":"環保"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:00:11.000Z","msg":"啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd1f1100de468b26a29cd69c747c90a0adc5831","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:00:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"276177b8eb45804144916e9f7e55da43c02c08f1","tid":1916294,"uid":42764,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:01:43.000Z","msg":"班環保撚靜曬既，收膠袋稅，扔電器收錢又咁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad243ff4261f0bea270d4162d0cfa248d6a71db1","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:01:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49be16331ffd1dc1e82d7648883c7e787658f927","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:02:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d1fe477c8458f127c53f951abda907aa001a6b8","tid":1916294,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"用口罩仲自私，應該留俾醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad35d68371eb0f8b500703474a3e3e902877700","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:03:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b987416c27c7e7fd35e675ab172580dbd2c8d36f","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:04:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f08654f6c0546d1b139b23e7f34686bb578ae5c","tid":1916294,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:04:17.000Z","msg":"任何幫到手足既都g持"},{"pid":"654e354029603ca62c7e2479a0008301084df9c0","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:05:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05a27ce3f98f66baf104d9758c167a10049ecb93","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44c2b88104e67ce927d22d53b4872661131643ae","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:06:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5025049cd1a818841908195179db181aa578563a","tid":1916294,"uid":32818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0a3ca34b0317dfaa528e09a75c39232c6620dda","tid":1916294,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:58:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:07:31.000Z","msg":"你放tg大撚把人搵你"},{"pid":"a246b9a75d1b4bb06111400c701a95e49fefabfe","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3149a2c9f3356b912002a4fe045ce407df1f5606","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62982825b8857db3f5adc7043d09ed62e9374e23","tid":1916294,"uid":250773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:09:40.000Z","msg":"n95無氣密點解衰過冇戴"},{"pid":"95a43d9b0a911eaf27bd1cddbd620ca60d1ee634","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"62982825b8857db3f5adc7043d09ed62e9374e23","tid":1916294,"uid":250773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:09:40.000Z","msg":"n95無氣密點解衰過冇戴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:11:45.000Z","msg":"[前線醫護有野講] N95戴錯衰過唔戴！用返普通口罩啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1815627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1815627</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c8ab84a10889dad74ef4ed67afc70df17376e8c","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:12:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"188af9543a00d100281845e0e8cfe014194d5ade","tid":1916294,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e98371b466e51419fc3164ae83f0b2c419dde1","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aecfcb29707ce935ca5792c5807886f2c7cbf1e0","tid":1916294,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:17:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n一個月前我咁講  有人留言話保命緊要過保護手足"},{"pid":"dd48f6a6ab1bacaca6c8c52e7b9ea41414766971","tid":1916294,"uid":11883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:45:08.000Z","msg":"係好多好處 但都要正確使用下先得<br />\n口罩勝在即棄 豬嘴用完要做返disinfection<br />\n<br />\n識用嘅轉用豬嘴會慳好多"},{"pid":"c32e6dc0d39b09a3643f0b3ed6f09cd7eaa94f1e","tid":1916294,"uid":129044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T21:13:46.000Z","msg":"有印像睇過 7093 嘅P100棉係襟用過6092x系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3d9989bcfb861d032c4b8e2899861d2e95edd9","tid":1916294,"uid":2027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T21:23:25.000Z","msg":"平時好易出汗所以選擇豬嘴....<br />\n帶口罩呼氣果下啲熱氣供哂上頭頂同臉<br />\n呢個天氣真心頂唔順<br />\n帶豬嘴真係舒服好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過番工冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2819cc83410ea32246b322ed1e01ebd255907fff","tid":1916294,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0a3ca34b0317dfaa528e09a75c39232c6620dda","tid":1916294,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:58:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T22:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a06d3c69a29bf361e8c7e8016a63540b422090","tid":1916294,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"豬嘴要完整清潔好難好麻煩<br />\n戴同除都要每掂一樣野洗一次手<br />\n老實講 我唔信有幾多人會做足<br />\n都係唔支持未到山窮水盡用豬嘴"},{"pid":"099e5fcdc2b8e06db9a37a93efe7165b8e024769","tid":1916294,"uid":341865,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T23:44:22.000Z","msg":"非常認同<br />\n但要正正經經用返p100 filter<br />\n唔好學例如城寨果啲傻閪用啲乜撚野剪口罩氣密蓋"},{"pid":"6cc7b7d4696457b3890bb55f4050d85d34ba3b6d","tid":1916294,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1fe477c8458f127c53f951abda907aa001a6b8","tid":1916294,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"用口罩仲自私，應該留俾醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T23:50:52.000Z","msg":"醫護唔用得自己口罩㗎，醫院唔撚批准<br />\n你送幾多口罩都無用"},{"pid":"1ce5b0a8cf91195cbcd96442d51be566158f9cfe","tid":1916294,"uid":57532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T23:55:36.000Z","msg":"環保撚出嚟講兩句啦，依家一日一個口罩好唔環保，製做緊幾多垃圾，要幾多年先分解晒。強烈建議帶豬嘴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac9a2b23f00c80d990a6772b719573008468445","tid":1916294,"uid":59804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"48a06d3c69a29bf361e8c7e8016a63540b422090","tid":1916294,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"豬嘴要完整清潔好難好麻煩<br />\n戴同除都要每掂一樣野洗一次手<br />\n老實講 我唔信有幾多人會做足<br />\n都係唔支持未到山窮水盡用豬嘴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T00:01:14.000Z","msg":"本身外科口罩都應該除同戴都要洗一次手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71eaf71c0e066f6bd645a097d981d9263a561309","tid":1916294,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T00:53:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0075323c609091308d08a220aa9880aaea386ea7","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64a3a76f961d42b112d725cb91e8ca6ab03d793e","tid":1916294,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"豬嘴其實係舒服過口罩"},{"pid":"3dfffc2594e8bdc1e6b7d499c7c8b4558dffda40","tid":1916294,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401269c8223cbf29a51cd8530f0c9a22b61f5a09","tid":1916294,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee22d69b0269d7d8d7d3e0902b01cc86963d6892","tid":1916294,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:28:19.000Z","msg":"上一個禮拜咀同罐都唔係貴到仆街<br />\namazon價, 7502 $29.9美金,有小小炒<br />\n60926 $28.95一對,正常價"},{"pid":"6d70aa48e5cecf3a2dace534f920aed0350c7b74","tid":1916294,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0142e74a966fa8aae30a520713387874675b537e","tid":1916294,"uid":10150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:15:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18806ecca052460376c1c99132bd400d5050c2f1","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c7025320547197f71157e2b974e2a1401501467","tid":1916294,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db2e68c9ab9e9cc9b8d46bcc33fa1e8f884bfe5a","tid":1916294,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ac9a2b23f00c80d990a6772b719573008468445","tid":1916294,"uid":59804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"48a06d3c69a29bf361e8c7e8016a63540b422090","tid":1916294,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"豬嘴要完整清潔好難好麻煩<br />\n戴同除都要每掂一樣野洗一次手<br />\n老實講 我唔信有幾多人會做足<br />\n都係唔支持未到山窮水盡用豬嘴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T00:01:14.000Z","msg":"本身外科口罩都應該除同戴都要洗一次手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"豬嘴有兩隻罐一個嘴多個扣位"},{"pid":"4a53c24938d545a3f5cbb4daf74fb875a0c5277b","tid":1916294,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd90240b20d9513c005322a19dc403ade80bba0a","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:56:46.000Z","msg":"呢兩日見倒幾個po話唔好戴豬嘴出街，話同口罩一鳩樣但又可能會招致<span style=\"color: red;\">殺身之禍。呢點我理解嘅，不過喺度唔放大縮細討論，大家自行衡量。</span>不過喺防疫方面只要正確使用，generally豬咀有潛質係個更好嘅選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 氣密性超班</span></strong></span><br />\n平時睇到啲外科口罩標示<span style=\"color: gold;\">BFE PFE VFE 99%</span>甚至以上，係咪覺得佢哋好勁呢? 咁當然唔係話口罩無效啦。但係知唔知道個test係點做? <span style=\"color: violet;\">係對正個罩嚟做架!</span> 飛沫可以繞過口罩正面，從4個方向進入並且污染口罩內部甚至吸入體內。如果個測試啲飛沫係由唔同方向射向口罩嘅話，個<span style=\"color: violet;\">過濾率可以得番7,8成架咋</span>!<br />\n至於N95，有用開嘅人都知道係要做fit test先知要咩size，而且唔易戴得啱、唔易做到真正氣密!<br />\n但豬嘴嘅設計因為<span style=\"color: gold;\">彈性嘅塑膠/矽膠設計</span>，大部份人用都可以容易達致氣密效果，而且仲唔會有口罩超常見嘅上方鐵線位漏氣嘅問題。只有喺氣密嘅情況下，果個filter嘅efficiency，先真正等於個filter自身嘅efficiency!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 價錢</span></strong></span><br />\n覺得豬嘴肯定貴? 隻價偏貴我駁唔倒啦，但其實大家留意吓，而家網上啲口罩都炒到<span style=\"color: red;\">至少5蚊隻以上</span>，連運費<span style=\"color: red;\">破40蚊</span>嘅我都見過。防護用N95呢，<span style=\"color: red;\">1x蚊隻以上</span>係基本啦。而且仲係要日日換，甚至濕起上嚟一日用兩個，條數其實都好甘。良心貨唔係無，但大家都知真係買少見少，全部大排長龍，我就一定留畀啲有需要人士呀，老人家果啲先。<br />\n豬嘴而家都炒。但學袁教授話齋，唔到年尾都唔好唔戴，果個可以清潔重用嘅嘴雖然都炒到3百幾，但圍番起當你2蚊日好未? 至於個filter，以都係炒到3百幾4百蚊一對嘅60926為例，當你雙嘴用四星期，畀夠你400蚊，除番都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">每日15蚊</span>。以高防嚟講其實真係唔算貴呀! <span style=\"color: gold;\">(另外我知最近有人批3D印緊啲可以剪外科口罩filter擺入去用嘅3M豬嘴filter匣，都係幾十蚊一對。因為可以將一片口罩剪開多次用，價錢將會抵過口罩，但同時因為氣密緣故防禦力又高過口罩!)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 豬嘴係自私道具?</span></strong></span><br />\n當然豬嘴有一個大家都知嘅問題，就係佢哋好多嘅設計個出氣口係經另一閥而唔經filter，所以如果你係隱形患者，咁香港人就真係多得你唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 目前由於3M豬嘴出氣口設計各異，所以(好似係)仲未有人開發倒出氣口嘅filter匣，但其實大家係可以用番上面個方法，搵一片剪啱size形狀嘅外科口罩喺個出口位度貼實佢。 (我唔係專家，但以防droplets嚟講，咁樣都應該係有效嘅?)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">4. 舒適度</span></strong></span><br />\n我覺得似乎個個人嘅感覺唔同，我都不便一口咬定，但我真係覺得豬嘴係最舒服嘅。首先N95就一定係好唔舒服嘅，因為出入都會經過個高阻力嘅filter。我自己戴半個鐘經已覺得好難頂。(你覺得戴N95抖氣好順暢? 恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無氣密，衰過無戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 但豬嘴就相對通風相當好，至少呼氣一定好順暢，而我自己覺得吸氣都只係差無戴嘴少少 (有test氣密，無漏氣的)。外科口罩有時會搞到我面頰同埋個鼻好痕，同埋眼鏡經常起霧。所以我個人rating一定係豬嘴第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">5. 保護手足</span></strong></span><br />\n呢個大家應該明，我就唔畫出腸喇。越多人戴越好。<br />\n<br />\n小小建議<br />\n希望能夠入手嘅都可以考慮下用豬嘴<br />\n記得做好清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面好多懶人包我就唔再詳細講喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"剪口罩放出條口我試過<br />\n呼氣時係會整到個嘴離開塊面影響氣密的<br />\n因為佢設計唔係for 你出氣口有阻力"},{"pid":"ba9ec4fbd23fbe065a17291013cf7103c7961567","tid":1916294,"uid":259079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"而家係街都開始見到多左人戴豬咀..."},{"pid":"4c203b31a15bfc7e1113f4b121502e000318fa2d","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a53c24938d545a3f5cbb4daf74fb875a0c5277b","tid":1916294,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd90240b20d9513c005322a19dc403ade80bba0a","tid":1916294,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T18:5